summary: CC partners with SRF to expand global supply chain, boost operational flexibility and strengthen its high-value product mix.

headline: Steel Dynamics to Acquire Remaining Stake in New Process Steel
summary: STLD moves to acquire full ownership of New Process Steel, expanding its U.S. and Mexico footprint with six plants and 1,275 employees.
